        whyEn: "This is a watershed moment for AI security capabilities. A model autonomously discovering thousands of zero-days means AI has reached superhuman level on both offense and defense. Anthropic's choice to restrict access rather than release publicly is a benchmark for 'responsible AI deployment.' For the security industry, this changes vulnerability discovery economics — work that took top security teams months, AI can now automate. For all software companies, patching speed must keep up with AI's vulnerability discovery rate.",
